WEBVTT

00:00:19.162 --> 00:00:24.349
笙ｪThe whole world is lit up笙ｪ

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:25.661
笙ｪBecause you exist笙ｪ

00:00:25.662 --> 00:00:27.741
笙ｪYou're always笙ｪ

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:32.391
笙ｪSomewhere close, flying with me笙ｪ

00:00:32.392 --> 00:00:35.124
笙ｪGo to where the wind blows笙ｪ

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:36.691
笙ｪHold tight笙ｪ

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:42.481
笙ｪTo the ray of light that belongs to us笙ｪ

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.907
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 12=

00:00:48.225 --> 00:00:50.295
(Inpatient Department VIP Ward)

00:01:06.580 --> 00:01:07.420
Where's my dad?

00:01:07.859 --> 00:01:09.019
He just passed away.

00:01:09.020 --> 00:01:10.819
He was fine earlier.

00:01:11.219 --> 00:01:13.099
How could he suddenly die?

00:01:13.979 --> 00:01:15.340
Was this your doing?

00:01:19.820 --> 00:01:21.338
How could you think that of me?

00:01:21.339 --> 00:01:23.900
He may be your father,
but he's also my husband.

00:01:24.499 --> 00:01:26.299
We're married.

00:01:26.380 --> 00:01:27.700
How could I possibly harm him?

00:01:27.820 --> 00:01:28.900
Besides,

00:01:29.259 --> 00:01:31.980
your dad died
after he was handed over to you.

00:01:32.339 --> 00:01:33.819
What does that have to do with me?

00:01:34.059 --> 00:01:38.058
Xu Mingzhu, don't think you can
brush this off with a few words.

00:01:38.059 --> 00:01:39.260
I'm telling you,

00:01:39.779 --> 00:01:40.980
I'll investigate

00:01:41.259 --> 00:01:43.420
my dad's death.

00:01:43.580 --> 00:01:44.780
Zhiyu,

00:01:45.859 --> 00:01:48.140
I understand how you feel right now.

00:01:48.612 --> 00:01:50.418
But the dead can't come back.

00:01:50.419 --> 00:01:52.060
Stop tormenting yourself.

00:01:52.380 --> 00:01:53.539
Also,

00:01:54.180 --> 00:01:55.338
your dad probably wouldn't want

00:01:55.339 --> 00:01:56.819
to see you like this.

00:01:57.859 --> 00:01:59.099
You're afraid, aren't you?

00:02:01.740 --> 00:02:04.060
Afraid I'll find evidence
that's bad for you.

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:10.620
If thinking of me as the villain
makes you feel better,

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:13.580
then I'll bear that accusation

00:02:13.939 --> 00:02:15.139
for now.

00:02:18.325 --> 00:02:22.099
(Inpatient Department VIP Ward)

00:02:22.100 --> 00:02:23.619
Has the body been dealt with?

00:02:24.300 --> 00:02:25.699
Yes.

00:02:25.819 --> 00:02:27.580
They won't be able to find anything.

00:02:27.619 --> 00:02:28.379
Good.

00:02:28.900 --> 00:02:30.740
Then we have nothing to worry about.

00:02:30.779 --> 00:02:32.058
Let's see what tricks

00:02:32.059 --> 00:02:34.020
Mu Zhiyu can still come up with.

00:02:53.499 --> 00:02:55.979
I didn't even get to see him
one last time.

00:02:57.659 --> 00:03:00.139
Dad's just gone like that.

00:03:02.539 --> 00:03:04.780
I remember when I was little,

00:03:05.260 --> 00:03:08.139
I was playful and I broke
his favorite Qing-Dynasty teacup.

00:03:09.100 --> 00:03:11.460
He held the broken pieces
for a long time, completely stunned.

00:03:11.499 --> 00:03:13.340
But in the end, he comforted me instead.

00:03:14.420 --> 00:03:15.780
(It's just a cup.)

00:03:16.140 --> 00:03:18.220
(As long as my daughter is safe.)

00:03:24.580 --> 00:03:26.699
Back then, I insisted on
studying auctioneering.

00:03:28.219 --> 00:03:30.220
Mom strongly opposed it.

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:33.620
She said it wasn't proper for a girl
to put herself in the public eye.

00:03:35.819 --> 00:03:38.740
Only he secretly helped me
gather materials and used his contacts.

00:03:41.140 --> 00:03:43.500
The day he sent me to the airport
to leave for the UK,

00:03:43.639 --> 00:03:45.480
I saw him wiping away tears
at the security gate.

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:47.020
But he still smiled

00:03:47.219 --> 00:03:49.539
and waved at me,
"Go chase your dreams.

00:03:50.420 --> 00:03:52.340
I'll wait for you to come back.

00:03:52.700 --> 00:03:54.498
Come back shining.

00:03:54.499 --> 00:03:56.939
And show everyone that you can do it."

00:03:58.300 --> 00:04:00.699
All these years,
I kept thinking about proving myself.

00:04:02.180 --> 00:04:03.259
I was wrong.

00:04:07.979 --> 00:04:10.740
I never even made a phone call to him.

00:04:11.180 --> 00:04:13.299
He always said, "If you're busy,
don't worry about home."

00:04:13.300 --> 00:04:15.580
And I took that seriously like a fool.

00:04:17.739 --> 00:04:19.020
But now...

00:04:19.739 --> 00:04:20.940
What should I do?

00:04:23.140 --> 00:04:24.940
I still have so many things

00:04:26.339 --> 00:04:28.099
I never got to say.

00:04:28.787 --> 00:04:31.020
So many reunion dinners we never had.

00:04:33.387 --> 00:04:35.539
So many hugs that never happened.

00:04:35.859 --> 00:04:38.020
So many achievements
I wanted to show him.

00:04:39.900 --> 00:04:41.179
But now,

00:04:42.299 --> 00:04:44.099
it all seems meaningless.

00:04:47.419 --> 00:04:49.659
I'm an orphan now.

00:05:02.940 --> 00:05:03.859
No.

00:05:05.580 --> 00:05:07.099
You're not alone.

00:05:07.859 --> 00:05:09.499
I'll always stay by your side.

00:05:10.312 --> 00:05:11.858
笙ｪThe wind blows across the wilderness笙ｪ

00:05:11.859 --> 00:05:14.218
I'll protect you
on Chairman Mu's behalf

00:05:14.219 --> 00:05:15.979
and help you fulfill all your wishes.

00:05:17.037 --> 00:05:19.024
笙ｪLike your silhouette笙ｪ

00:05:19.025 --> 00:05:22.978
笙ｪSlowly swallowed by the sunset笙ｪ

00:05:22.979 --> 00:05:24.820
Why are you helping me so much?

00:05:26.550 --> 00:05:29.320
笙ｪThe corner of abandoned time笙ｪ

00:05:30.025 --> 00:05:32.549
笙ｪI watch the stars in your eyes笙ｪ

00:05:32.550 --> 00:05:35.420
笙ｪFall one by one笙ｪ

00:05:38.500 --> 00:05:41.111
笙ｪI saw you when the wind blew笙ｪ

00:05:41.112 --> 00:05:44.582
笙ｪLike a sign across mountains and seas笙ｪ

00:05:45.739 --> 00:05:47.539
(Because we're the same.)

00:05:47.659 --> 00:05:49.299
(I understand your pain.)

00:05:49.620 --> 00:05:51.260
(I understand your frustration.)

00:05:51.900 --> 00:05:53.099
(Can I really)

00:05:53.339 --> 00:05:55.580
(trust this embrace?)

00:05:55.779 --> 00:05:57.059
(I want to protect you)

00:05:57.179 --> 00:05:59.019
(and protect the younger me too.)

00:05:59.020 --> 00:06:00.924
笙ｪA journey with no end笙ｪ

00:06:00.925 --> 00:06:02.674
笙ｪBut in my heart笙ｪ

00:06:02.675 --> 00:06:04.683
笙ｪYour name is forever carved笙ｪ

00:06:23.620 --> 00:06:26.340
I finished off Mu Chenzhou for you.

00:06:26.620 --> 00:06:28.020
How are you going to reward me?

00:06:29.375 --> 00:06:31.374
I can give you anything you want.

00:06:34.419 --> 00:06:35.859
Patience.

00:06:37.179 --> 00:06:38.338
Right now,

00:06:38.339 --> 00:06:40.739
we have more important things
to deal with.

00:06:41.859 --> 00:06:43.499
Once Mu Chenzhou is dead,

00:06:43.662 --> 00:06:46.749
Mu Zhiyu will naturally become
the rightful heir.

00:06:46.750 --> 00:06:48.418
Are we just going to watch

00:06:48.419 --> 00:06:50.019
as she gets the company

00:06:50.020 --> 00:06:51.659
and inherits everything?

00:06:51.940 --> 00:06:53.580
The sooner she inherits it, the better.

00:06:54.060 --> 00:06:55.738
Once that brat gets the inheritance,

00:06:55.739 --> 00:06:58.299
she'll definitely use the key
to open the safe.

00:06:58.580 --> 00:06:59.418
At that point,

00:06:59.419 --> 00:07:02.780
our pawn Shen Jibai
can take advantage of the situation.

00:07:03.739 --> 00:07:05.900
Then both the company
and the inheritance will be ours.

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:22.539
Yu,

00:07:23.219 --> 00:07:27.099
I'm sorry for your loss.
Please take care of yourself.

00:07:27.299 --> 00:07:28.299
I'm fine.

00:07:28.580 --> 00:07:29.538
Don't worry.

00:07:29.539 --> 00:07:30.499
As long as I'm here,

00:07:30.500 --> 00:07:31.499
no matter what happens,

00:07:31.500 --> 00:07:32.619
you can tell me.

00:07:32.620 --> 00:07:33.659
I'll help you.

00:07:35.500 --> 00:07:36.580
I suspect

00:07:36.940 --> 00:07:39.020
Xu Mingzhu is behind my dad's death.

00:07:39.900 --> 00:07:41.859
But I don't have any evidence.

00:07:44.539 --> 00:07:45.658
No matter what,

00:07:45.659 --> 00:07:47.460
we must find out the truth.

00:07:47.779 --> 00:07:48.940
The priority now

00:07:49.020 --> 00:07:50.780
is to figure out

00:07:50.859 --> 00:07:53.059
what Xu Mingzhu is plotting.

00:07:54.512 --> 00:07:55.832
Whatever she's trying to do,

00:07:56.140 --> 00:07:57.940
I won't let her succeed.

00:08:05.739 --> 00:08:08.299
- Then I'll leave it to you, Mr. Wang.
- Okay. Don't worry.

00:08:08.460 --> 00:08:09.859
You're back, Zhiyu.

00:08:10.225 --> 00:08:12.105
Mr. Wang has been waiting for you.

00:08:12.779 --> 00:08:13.940
Hello, Ms. Mu.

00:08:14.060 --> 00:08:16.539
I'm the personal lawyer
for the Mu family.

00:08:18.299 --> 00:08:19.619
What's the matter?

00:08:22.260 --> 00:08:23.220
Ms. Mu,

00:08:23.339 --> 00:08:24.338
before Mr. Mu passed away,

00:08:24.339 --> 00:08:25.858
he entrusted me with a will.

00:08:25.859 --> 00:08:28.280
He asked me to personally deliver it
to you after his death.

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:30.220
You're here about my dad's will?

00:08:30.580 --> 00:08:31.299
Yes.

00:08:39.100 --> 00:08:39.979
Ms. Mu,

00:08:40.299 --> 00:08:41.619
Mr. Mu specifically instructed

00:08:41.620 --> 00:08:43.139
that you must fulfill his last wish.

00:08:43.140 --> 00:08:44.019
Only then

00:08:44.020 --> 00:08:45.580
will you be able to inherit his estate.

00:08:45.587 --> 00:08:47.348
(No matter what the will says,)

00:08:47.699 --> 00:08:49.899
(Mu Group must belong to me.)

00:09:05.075 --> 00:09:09.305
笙ｪLight comes beaming in笙ｪ

00:09:09.445 --> 00:09:13.814
笙ｪLanding on my skin笙ｪ

00:09:13.815 --> 00:09:18.305
笙ｪWarms the space you left behind笙ｪ

00:09:22.525 --> 00:09:26.464
笙ｪShadows move around笙ｪ

00:09:26.465 --> 00:09:31.074
笙ｪAwake, racing thoughts笙ｪ

00:09:31.075 --> 00:09:35.605
笙ｪTry to keep the memories safe笙ｪ

00:09:39.205 --> 00:09:44.995
笙ｪDon't slip away笙ｪ

00:09:47.445 --> 00:09:52.014
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:09:52.015 --> 00:09:56.414
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:09:56.415 --> 00:10:00.735
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:10:00.755 --> 00:10:04.735
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:10:05.205 --> 00:10:09.514
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:10:09.515 --> 00:10:13.844
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:10:13.845 --> 00:10:18.154
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

00:10:18.155 --> 00:10:24.305
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ